targets.query: Select last(confirmed) as time, time as timestamp from covid19
SELECT sum("confirmed") AS "Confirmed" FROM "covid19" WHERE ("state" =~ /^$States$/ AND "county" =~ /^$County$/) AND time > now() - 1d GROUP BY time(1d), "geohash", "location" fill(none)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT timestamp AS "time", geohash AS "geohash", confirmed AS "Confirmed", name AS "location" FROM bases
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(timestamp)
ORDER BY timestamp
